Property.Name: BodyScript
HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT A.* FROM Actor A, FilmActor FM, Film F WHERE A.ActorId = FM.ActorId and FM.FilmId = F.FilmId and F.Title = UPPER(@FilmTitle) END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT * FROM Actor WHERE ActorId = @Id END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT * FROM Actor WHERE LEFT(FirstName,1) = @FirstL and LEFT(LastName,1) = @LastL END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT * FROM Actor WHERE SUBSTRING(LastName,1,1) = @LastL END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT * FROM Film f , Actor a , FilmActor fa where a.ActorId = fa.ActorId AND f.FilmId = fa.FilmId AND a.LastName = @LastName; RETURN 0

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT * FROM Film f, Category c, FilmCategory fc WHERE f.FilmId = fc.FilmId AND c.CategoryId = fc.CategoryId AND c.[Name] = @catName; END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT * FROM Film WHERE [Description] Like '%' + @KeyWord +'%' RETURN 0

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT * from Film f , [Language] l where f.LanguageId = l.LanguageId AND l.[Name] = @Language RETURN 0

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT * From Film where Title LIKE '%' + @Title + '%' RETURN 0
